Sam attached the console output (Output.txt) when running build.xml directly since it provides more info. [~marvin07ro] Could you try the following:

1. Right-click on the build.xml file under project and select Run As > Ant Build...;
2. Select Properties tab and uncheck the option "Use global properties...";
3. Click on "Add Properties..." and put "android.ndk" for the name and your Android NDK location for the value;
4. Hit "Run".

Attaching the resulted output here will be very helpful.

Thanks.

